Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:42.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98119,102749}I've caught you, St. Tail!\NYou won't get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109380,110632}Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111507,112592}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:58.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113468,118014}So you were the thief, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119641,122477}You had me fooled all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122935,126939}No, no. I wasn't fooling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:11.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127857,131903}All this time I just couldn't\Nget myself to tell you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135239,137367}A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:24.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141120,144499}Ruby, I just can't get myself\Nto tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147627,150630}…that I'm St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:39.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154175,159263}I definitely can't tell him.\NAnd I definitely can't let him catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:45.26,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:161015,165269}A Fake Calling Card!?\NThe Secret of the Perfume Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169107,170233}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177907,179117}Addressed to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179117,182120}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184288,186624}Is it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186624,189335}Aren't the girls putting\Nextra effort into their hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189335,191587}Yep. And here's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:17.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192171,197552}A cosmetic company is looking for\Na girl to introduce their new shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:22.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198094,202724}Sawatari says that he's taking\Na photo to compete in the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202724,204559}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204559,206936}Well, just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:31.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206936,211482}These hands will be sending\Na supermodel into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212150,215445}Meimi, look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216195,219907}Nothing different.\NJust doing his same old stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220366,222368}It's Meimi, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222368,225872}How can you fight it?\NShe's got beautiful hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226205,230460}St. Tail's hair is\Na hundred times prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230460,232837}You don't change either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236340,237884}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237884,240762}Speak of the devil!\NIt's a notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241095,242764}What will it be this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:07.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244265,247226}– Let me have a look!\N– What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:13.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248102,253691}"Tomorrow night I will be stealing\Nthe Parfum Takarada Special. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254525,257320}She's going after some perfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257320,259155}So that's the next caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:25.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259530,265119}{\i1}What's this supposed to mean?\NI didn't send this notice. Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268456,271626}Why are you in such deep prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274045,276631}You look very depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277590,280593}I have just lost my father\Nin an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281260,283346}I'm very sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283346,285890}My father was a perfumer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285890,289101}He developed fragrances\Nfor perfumes, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289101,290812}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290812,294690}Before his death, he mentioned\Na new perfume that was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294690,297527}And he was very happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297819,300530}{\i1}A perfume?\NCould it be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:05.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300738,305993}But just before it was to be completed,\Nhe got into a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:12.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308246,312667}When Father died, he had\Na notebook clenched in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312667,316796}The notebook contained the formula\Nfor his new perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:21.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316796,321425}Your father passionately loved\Nhis work until the very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:27.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321676,327098}Yes, but the final ingredient\Nwasn't written in the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327098,330393}Now that he's gone,\Nwe don't have any idea what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:34.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330393,334397}Oh, my.\NYou don't have a single clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:38.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334897,338818}The last entry in the notebook\Nwas "Earring of Snow".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338818,341362}But it was written like a secret code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:45.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342113,345324}It's probably a flower\Nthat blossoms in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346617,350288}Were you in deep prayer trying\Nto find out what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:55.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350788,355376}Oh, no! I will definitely complete\NFather's perfume on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355376,358254}That's not what is troubling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:05.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361299,365219}I ask for God's help,\Nfor the sake of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365887,367221}Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:12.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368514,372184}After Father's death, my brother\Nhas become a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:18.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372935,378149}He doesn't care about the perfume,\Nonly about how much he can sell it for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378608,381611}He is planning\Nan outrageous scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389243,391037}This is the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391037,394540}This is where we raise flowers and\Nconcoct ingredients for the perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:41.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397168,401547}And this is the Parfum\NTakarada Special, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402423,406510}We haven't mass-produced it yet,\Nso this is the only bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406969,409430}For St. Tail to crave this,\Nshe must see its true value.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410348,412391}Please leave the security to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:58.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414268,418397}Let's make the security a big thing,\Nas extravagant as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:02.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418898,422109}As extravagant as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:08.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422777,428074}I'm selling this to a major\Nmanufacturer in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429367,433037}It would be a disaster\Nif it gets stolen before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433746,435081}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:20.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435790,440044}In any case, it's a product\Nthat's sure to be a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440962,442046}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:28.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443839,448010}{\i1}It'll be a smash hit with the help\Nof our little St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448636,451639}A St. Tail brand perfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:38.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452807,458938}That fake notice was probably sent\Nby Miss Takarada's brother to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459271,460940}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:46.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461482,466654}He is trying to sell an incomplete\Nperfume formula for a high price
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:50.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466654,470908}by advertising it as "a perfume\Nworth being stolen by St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471867,473911}What a dirty trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:08:01.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473911,481419}His sister, Yuriko, says that she's against sending\Nthe incomplete formula out on the market
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481419,484255}and deceiving people\Nwith false advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:07.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485047,487925}I'd really like to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487925,490177}Meimi, you'll do it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:14.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490177,494306}Of course. Let's make the best\Nof that fake calling card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:20.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496809,500730}Well, now, let's begin\Nour long homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500730,503232}Oh, the petals are falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503232,504400}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504400,506277}The cherry blossoms in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506277,508612}Will the flowers hold\Nuntil school is out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508696,510364}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510364,513617}Oh, my goodness. Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:38.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513617,518789}We'll have you go out to play\Nin the yard for this hour of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521292,524045}Just for this hour now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524795,528382}Really, they're supposed\Nto be junior high students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528382,530843}Is it the season\Nor do they just want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:09:00.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535806,540186}Sawatari, how could you bring\Nyour camera at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540186,543939}You amateur,\Nit's in beautiful scenery like this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543939,545900}when true beauty\Ncan be photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546776,548819}Hey, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548819,550863}The same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551781,555826}Where's the difference?\NHaneoka looks the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556702,558788}– Meimi, come, come!\N– What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:27.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563626,567630}What's wrong with me?\NThat's totally impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567630,569340}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570091,571926}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:36.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572510,576097}There's something\NI want to ask you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576097,579934}Do you know what the secret code\N"Earring of Snow" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579934,581852}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:46.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581852,586190}{\i1}Asuka Jr. knows a lot of things.\NHe just might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:50.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586899,590236}So winter flowers,\Nwhat kind are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:54.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590236,594156}I don't know anything about flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595991,598577}There's just one I've heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598577,601205}When I was 5 years old,\Nmy mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601205,602581}Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603624,606544}I think it's a story that\Ngoes back to the Creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608170,609505}The Creation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609964,613467}Well, a story that\Ngoes way back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:19.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615970,619431}Everything in nature\Nhas a color, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620141,623602}Just as the sky is blue\Nand the clouds are gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623602,626814}Well, the snow went to see God,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:31.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626814,631610}and told him,\N"It's unfair that I have no color".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:40.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633946,640161}God told the snow,\N"Ask a flower to give you its color".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:44.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640161,644373}But there wasn't a single flower that\Nwould give the cold snow its color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644373,645875}How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:49.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645875,649461}But, just as the snow was\Nabout to give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:54.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649461,654049}a flower came forth and said,\N"You can have my white color".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654049,655301}Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:11:02.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655926,662600}Since then, it's said that the snow\Nprotects that small flower during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664643,668731}That's got to be it!\NWhat's the name of that flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670733,672610}I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673944,677656}I know it was\Na delicious-sounding name but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678407,681744}Oh, boy! You're hopeless\Nat the crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682411,684246}Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698135,701847}What are you all worked up over?\NIt's just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:46.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702514,706435}I want to know about the flower\Nthat is able to survive near snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:52.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706852,712274}{\i1}I can't tell him I'm St. Tail.\NI definitely can't let him catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713150,716237}Thank you. Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718072,720199}What was that all about?
Comment: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:09.75,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:729750,729750}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:14.75,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:734755,734755}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735965,737258}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:22.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739260,742179}Welcome home.\NMeimi, come over here a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742471,744181}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:28.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745432,748811}Mother. Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748811,750020}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750020,751397}Here, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:37.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752106,757361}Strange. It's not my birthday or our\Nwedding anniversary, but a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757861,760322}Never mind, just open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767413,770624}What's this? You two are terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770624,773210}It's my new magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:57.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773544,777172}Oh, you! Just look at this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:02.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778215,782094}What? Snow? Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782094,783846}Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786140,789810}Papa, it's a great idea…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:14.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790060,794773}But isn't it a bit off-season for snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795107,797526}Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:23.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799028,803699}Oh! What am I going to do?\NThe dinner has…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805075,807786}I'm sorry, Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812750,816253}Meimi seemed depressed.\NI was trying to cheer her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816253,819631}I know. She was moaning\Nin her sleep last night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820049,822134}I wonder if something\Nhappened at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822384,825763}Don't worry.\NShe's our daughter after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826513,828098}She'll get herself back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828724,830768}I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841820,845491}Ruby, well, it's time to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:12.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846617,852414}{\i1}I won't, I won't…\NI can't let him catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853082,856377}Don't worry!\NI'm just fine. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:26.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862383,866345}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871350,872351}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874645,876021}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877981,880484}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:58.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894289,898752}Meimi, the flower that\NAsuka Jr. was talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898752,901922}it's probably called the snow drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901922,903507}How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:08.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904258,908971}It's the only winter flower\Nthat has a delicious-sounding name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909430,911932}I see! Thanks, Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914226,917938}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:29.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925737,929408}The perfume in Mr. Takarada's hand\Nis St. Tail's target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929408,930951}Let's keep the security tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930951,933245}Yes, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:40.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935038,940878}With this security alone, St. Tail\Nwill be associated with this perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:46.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941170,946842}Even if the notice is fake\Nand St. Tail doesn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947176,949052}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949052,950888}This woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950888,952431}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952431,954516}Yuriko! I told you to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955058,958479}Brother, please stop all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961815,963442}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964818,967905}Good evening!\NThank you for the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969156,970073}Invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970073,973118}This can't be! The notice is a—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973911,976038}Something wrong with the notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976038,977080}Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978207,981043}{\i1}Why is the real St. Tail here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981752,984505}{\i1}I'm the one that sent\Nthe fake calling card out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986507,987633}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988467,989510}Brother, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989927,991678}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:40.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995349,1000646}God sees through everything!\NOne! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012324,1014243}Hold it! That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017788,1019748}I'm leaving with the perfume!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019748,1021625}Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021625,1024962}Who will let you get away with it?\NWait! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025921,1027256}There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032761,1035973}Asuka Jr., the perfume!\NGet that perfume back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037766,1039935}Mr. Takarada, it's time\Nfor you to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041436,1043397}What's going on here, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050487,1051905}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053323,1055534}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056994,1058245}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066336,1068130}Asuka Jr., this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:53.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068505,1073093}What's happening?\NThe temperature is… It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073677,1075554}Is it her famous illusion trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:01.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076430,1081018}Stop! Father's flowers will die! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:07.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082561,1087941}If the flowers die, we won't be able\Nto make the perfume! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:16.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090902,1096658}Brother, it's your fault. If Father's\Nflowers die, it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100829,1103582}Yuriko, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105500,1106710}Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108045,1111965}You two will be able\Nto make a wonderful perfume,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111965,1114468}even without the use of my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115260,1118430}What are you blabbering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119222,1122392}Let's forget about it, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122809,1125354}But the perfume…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:49.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125896,1129316}That calling card, I was the one\Nwho sent it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:57.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131652,1137115}Instead of completing the perfume,\Nall I thought of was how to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:01.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137616,1141244}If St. Tail was after it,\Nit would become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141244,1142287}That's why I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142287,1143955}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:07.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143955,1147542}Asuka Jr., I should have gone\Nand told you of it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:14.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154007,1154966}Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157636,1160889}No, they're white flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167646,1170774}{\i1}The fragrance of this flower?\NCould it be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:35.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171108,1175737}The final ingredient in the notebook,\N"Earring of Snow", is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176196,1179074}We can make it! Father's perfume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179074,1182119}Yuriko, let's try\Nto complete it together!
